Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告訴你的事  是最高機密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I'm about to tell you is top secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Evil Corp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提利爾·威利克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tyrell Wellick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想一起嗑藥嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to do these together then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純搖頭丸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pure Molly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  夏拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Shayla. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得來趟眾安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to come to AllSafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死  他們進入網絡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit. They're in the network?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個  去社會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is it. Fsociety.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們叫我留著它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're telling me to leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你該跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you should come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那是達琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that's Darlene.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要修改那個dat文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are going to modify the dat file
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把科比的IP放進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}put Colby's IP in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你照做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就啟動了有史以來最大規模的革命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you have set in motion the largest revolution the world will ever see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息源確認黑客行為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sources have confirmed the hacks were
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與科比的終端有一定關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in part tied to Colby's terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生  請上車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, step inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bon soir, Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"給人一把槍  他就能搶銀行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Give a man a gun and he can rob a bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但給人一座銀行  他就能洗劫整個世界"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but give a man a bank, and he can rob the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.85,0:01:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這說法挺蠢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a bit of a silly expression, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點武斷了  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A little reductive, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大部分人討厭這說法的原因一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the same reason most people hate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我認為這話的意思是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because to me it means that 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,權力屬于肯去奪取的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}power belongs to the people that take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們的努力  強大的野心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing to do with their hard work, strong ambitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者資歷之類的都無關\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or rightful qualifications, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常  只有奪取的意愿才是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The actual will to take is often the only thing that's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉用這種方式把你帶過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to bring you in like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴格說  我們這樣做可能是違法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Technically what we're doing might be considered illegal,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我身邊才坐著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is why I'm surrounded
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11位最煩人的律師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by eleven of our most annoying lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾略特·奧德森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elliot Alderson...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想為你提供\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to offer you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡公司供職的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a position here at Evil Corp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你來主管我們的網絡安全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to head our cybersecurity division.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是由于我們和你的雇主  眾安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except I can't officially offer you anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有競業禁止協議  所以我不能正式聘用你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since we have this non-compete with your employer, Allsafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你能自愿跳槽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you do this of your own accord--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跳槽以后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you do this--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年內就能坐擁百萬家產\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'll be a multi-millionaire within the next five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能考慮一下嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生們  讓我們單獨談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gentlemen, I need the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  謝謝  謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, thank you. Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡公司剛任命我為臨時首席技術官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Evil Corp has just named me interim CTO.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過不了多久就會正式上任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It won't be long until it's official.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將會成為這家公司有史以來最年輕的高管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will be the youngest executive this company has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真應該找到那些黑客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should track down these hackers out there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以表謝意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just to thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可以說有點...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a way, it's kind of, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個詞怎么說來著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the word in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤打誤撞  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Serendipitous? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到本季度末\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, by the end of the quarter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們準備重新構建網絡系統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we're going to revamp our entire network
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并加固安全協議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and consolidate our security protocols.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情我們都會內部解決\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to handle everything internally,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我們會中止和所有供應商的合同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which means all of our vendors, including Allsafe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括眾安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will be cut loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾所周知  眾安沒了我們這個客戶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's no secret that once Allsafe loses us as a client,
