Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑客困境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hacker's dilemma. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如何摧毀完全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What to do when a bunch of data you want to destroy
