Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會殺人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not killing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me one thing, Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是1還是0\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you a one or a zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要問自己這個問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the question you have to ask yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是是還是否\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you a yes or a no?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.46,0:24:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要采取行動  還是無所作為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you going to act or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.27,0:24:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是玩電腦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yo...you've been staring at a computer screen
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.26,0:24:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩太久了  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}way too long, homie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活不是那么二進制的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Life's not that binary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.14,0:24:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.99,0:24:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  有灰色地帶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure, there are grays--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.25,0:24:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說到底  最根本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but when you come right down to it, at its core,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.42,0:24:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個決定  都是由1或0構成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}beneath every choice, there's either a one or a zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.46,0:24:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要么采取行動  要么什么不做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You either do something or you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.54,0:24:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走出那扇門  就是決定了要什么都不做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You walk out that door, you've decided to do nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.10,0:24:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定拒絕  那么你就不能再回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to say no, which means you do not come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.05,0:25:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走  就不再是這事的一員了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You leave, you are no longer a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.32,0:25:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是0了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You become a zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.32,0:25:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.02,0:25:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想改變世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you want to change the world,
