Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.27,0:25:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是1\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You become a one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.09,0:25:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再問你一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I'll ask you again:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.19,0:25:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是1還是0\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are you a one or a zero?
