Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.41,0:25:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了  別自欺欺人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, let's not kid ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.30,0:25:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟科比毫無關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This has nothing to do with Colby.
