Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.64,0:25:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你不僅是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is more than that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.57,0:25:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了那些混蛋慢慢地殺了你父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is about how those bastards slowly killed your father
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.31,0:25:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你希望他當初對此采取了行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and how you wished he'd done something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.02,0:25:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他沒有  因為他是0\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he didn't. Because he was a zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.91,0:25:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你現在這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just like you're being right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.31,0:25:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}F--- you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.46,0:25:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要玩消失嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disappearing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.34,0:25:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不殺人  你們別扯上我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not killing anyone. Leave me out of this.
