Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.01,0:28:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮過告發他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've thought about turning him in,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.77,0:28:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是夏拉唯一的供毒販\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he's Shayla's only supplier.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.80,0:28:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扳倒他  我也沒藥了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I take him down, I lose my drugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.04,0:28:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有那么多事  我不能失去藥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and with everything going on right now, I can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.30,0:28:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You get that, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.77,0:28:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyway, bro,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.35,0:28:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ain't nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.54,0:29:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是來給你送貨的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just making a drop for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.03,0:29:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your name, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.56,0:29:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.31,0:29:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.36,0:29:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從沒谷歌過嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you ain't never Googled it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.19,0:29:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去谷歌啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Man, you gotta do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.03,0:29:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人名字的含義是很重要的  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The meaning of a person's name is important, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.80,0:29:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事的  她沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yo, she good! She good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.93,0:29:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.87,0:29:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親自確保的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Took care of that shit myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.35,0:29:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我想起了我年輕一點的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remind me of me when I was younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.55,0:29:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓抑  陰沉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}depressed and sullen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.69,0:29:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  我還曾幾次試圖自殺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Matter of fact, tried to kill myself, a couple of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.64,0:29:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒做對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never could get that shit right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.80,0:29:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生物不是我的強項\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Biology wasn't my strong suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.34,0:29:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨自己  現在也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hated myself, man. Still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.31,0:29:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以來  覺得那是軟弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought that shit was a weakness for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.82,0:30:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我意識到  那是我的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I realized that shit was my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.38,0:30:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上的人  一副知道恨是什么的樣子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People walk around, act like they know what hate means.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.42,0:30:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒人知道  除非你恨自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah, no one does, until you hate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.97,0:30:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.43,0:30:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正恨自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}truly hate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.91,0:30:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.98,0:30:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ain't scared of me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.83,0:30:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不用浪費時間討好你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Means I didn't waste my time making friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.08,0:30:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不需要這個吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't really need these, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.40,0:30:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這么勇敢的人  能撐過戒癮的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Man of your courage can last through a little withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.09,0:30:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你  我才認識夏拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ya know, you the only reason why I met Shayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.48,0:30:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是市內唯一什么都賣的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the only nigga in town carrying everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.50,0:30:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括你的寶貝賽寶松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}including your precious Suboxone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.99,0:31:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  說來怪  但我該感謝你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, in a weird way, I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.00,0:31:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把她送到我身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You brought her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.70,0:31:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行星環繞我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your star orbiting with mine, gravitationally,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.48,0:31:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我帶來了我的摯愛  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}brought me the love of my life, Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.14,0:31:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, this, us?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.07,0:31:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里相見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Being here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.84,0:31:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這擁有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This has...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.10,0:31:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美妙的意義\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}beautiful meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.46,0:31:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但別誤會  那女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But make no mistake, that girl in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.35,0:31:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.65,0:31:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離了她我都不知道如何是好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what I'd do without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.24,0:31:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你們之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I don't know what kind of arrangement
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.86,0:31:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有怎樣的安排  但既然我們都是朋友了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you had with her before, but now that we friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.57,0:31:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你會知道朋友妻不可欺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I trust you respect this boundary.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.47,0:31:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feel me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.13,0:31:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早些時候也有個家伙這么看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A dude earlier today gave me that same look.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.31,0:31:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only thing I gotta say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.28,0:31:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候  還是害怕明智  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's a smart time to be scared, bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.07,0:32:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有時不明智\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a stupid time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.54,0:32:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.09,0:32:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撬鎖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The lock pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.82,0:32:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有黑客最鐘情的運動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every hacker's favorite sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.62,0:32:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最合適去破解的系統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The perfect system to crack,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.02,0:32:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是因為與虛擬系統不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}mostly because unlike virtual systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.09,0:32:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撬開它時  你能感覺到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you break it, you can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.94,0:32:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到  能聽到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can see it. You can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.44,0:32:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.29,0:32:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.68,0:32:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.54,0:32:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.46,0:32:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋怎么在這兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why was that asshole here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.64,0:32:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么在浴缸里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why am I in the tub?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.52,0:32:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  我告訴他  我需要你的藥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}I don't know, um...I told him I needed your pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.12,0:32:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就過來  我們抽了一會兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He came over. We smoked a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.76,0:33:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記得跟他做愛嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remember having sex with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.49,0:33:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.78,0:33:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他肯定記得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he definitely does.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.30,0:33:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.76,0:33:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-拿上你的包  一定...  -別說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get your purse, make sure-- - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.79,0:33:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪也不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.57,0:33:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.88,0:33:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要讓他逃脫罪責嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, he's just gonna get away with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.94,0:33:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再去找他了  我不需要那些藥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't go back to him. Hey, I don't need the pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.84,0:33:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-找別人試試吧  -我不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just find someone else. - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.65,0:33:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他給我的價錢很便宜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He gives me a really good deal on the split.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.20,0:33:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掙錢多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I make good money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.71,0:33:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There it is again,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.55,0:33:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個隱形之手在控制我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the invisible hand at work, controlling us,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.06,0:33:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使推我們越過了疼痛臨界點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even if it pushes us past our threshold of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.35,0:33:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不會停止的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not gonna stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.42,0:33:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他再這么做呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if he does it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.39,0:33:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應我你不會做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promise me you won't do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.94,0:33:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說真的  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm serious, Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.88,0:33:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么可做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing to be done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.33,0:33:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒什么選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not like I have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.96,0:34:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚能睡這里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you mind sleeping here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.99,0:34:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.77,0:34:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許機器人先生是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe Mr. Robot's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.97,0:34:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是一切的關鍵  生活中的同意和拒絕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what this is all about, the yesses and nos of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.06,0:34:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們做決定  還是決定左右我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But do we decide them or do they decide us?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.80,0:34:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費南多·維拉  我解決了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fernando Vera. I get rid of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.95,0:34:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就斷了我自己的毒品源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get rid of my drug dealer's supplier.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.29,0:34:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就斷了嗎啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get rid of the morphine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.97,0:34:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在控制的痛苦會一擁而上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the pain I've been holding in comes rushing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.56,0:34:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我可以再去找其他毒販\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure, I can try to find another dealer,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.20,0:34:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就像維拉所說  街面上沒人賣賽寶松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but like Vera said, no one on the streets deals Suboxone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.37,0:34:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回到電子偽造處方的手段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could go back to digitally counterfeiting scripts,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.82,0:34:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但藥房都花大錢保護他們的商品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but pharmas spend a lot of dough protecting their wares.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.85,0:34:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分地方只收紙質處方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most places only take paper scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.24,0:34:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一直拿到合法的處方是不現實的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Continuously getting legit refills isn't realistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.80,0:34:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做癮君子也一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and neither is being a junkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.80,0:34:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我要么直接戒斷  要么就放過維拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I quit cold turkey or let Vera exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.84,0:34:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在想什么  答案太簡單了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what you're thinking. The answer's too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.76,0:34:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉之前或許已經對夏拉動手動腳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vera may have been groping Shayla before,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.25,0:34:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在他已經升級至強奸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he's graduated to rape.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.64,0:35:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}費南多·維拉  早早哄入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.86,0:35:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟夏拉一樣  他讓我別無選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like Shayla, he's left me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.27,0:35:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能允許他再逍遙了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He can't be allowed to exist anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.44,0:35:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先說說你的感受吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we should start with how you're feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.88,0:35:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.64,0:35:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在什么不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's not good right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.61,0:35:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.79,0:35:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說細節吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Humor me with some specifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.37,0:35:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要如何知道你能掌控生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do we know if we're in control?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.85,0:35:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是對生活的困難\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That we're not just making the best
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.06,0:35:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡力而為  僅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of what comes at us, and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.03,0:36:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在兩個選項中二選其一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trying to constantly pick between two options.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.29,0:36:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你等候室里的兩幅畫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like your two paintings in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.19,0:36:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是  可樂還是百事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or...Coke and Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.60,0:36:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥當勞還是漢堡王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}McDonald's or Burger King?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.76,0:36:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現代還是本田\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hyundai or Honda?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.59,0:36:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}費南多·維拉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.84,0:36:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是模糊一片  不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all part of the same blur, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.14,0:36:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}唐人街暴力沖突升級  黑幫分子被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.30,0:36:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好對不上焦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just out of focus enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.64,0:36:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}紐約警局匿名檢舉熱線
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.30,0:36:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有選擇的幻覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the illusion of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.32,0:36:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}維拉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.93,0:36:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們半數人  甚至不能自己選\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half of us can't even pick our own--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.64,0:36:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}點擊"瀏覽"選擇文件與檢舉一同發送
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.07,0:36:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有線電視  煤氣  電力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our cable, gas, electric.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.70,0:36:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}多謝你協助保護紐約市安全
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.51,0:36:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們喝的水  我們的醫療保險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The water we drink, our health insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.94,0:36:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我們選的  又有什么用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if we did, would it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.17,0:36:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們只能在藍十字會和藍盾{\fs14}[均為醫療保險]{\fs}中選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, if our only option is Blue Cross or Blue Shield,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.49,0:36:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又有什么差別\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what the f--- is the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.29,0:36:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這倆不是一樣的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, aren't they-- aren't they the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.04,0:37:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.14,0:37:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的選擇早已經有定數了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our choices are prepaid for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.91,0:37:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就選好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.35,0:37:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾你感到無法控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry you feel you have no control.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.35,0:37:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我在做好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought I was doing something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.91,0:37:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我參與了一個項目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was a part of this... project.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.34,0:37:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我參與了一件特別的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought I was going to be a part of something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.79,0:37:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.82,0:37:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.67,0:37:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那是個錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It turned out to be a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.15,0:37:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像其他的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.69,0:37:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么意義\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.53,0:37:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不如  什么都不做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might as well, just-- you do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.81,0:37:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如什么都不做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might as well do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.56,0:37:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前也提過這個問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've brought up this issue before,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.22,0:38:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你無法控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this issue of not feeling like you're in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.56,0:38:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.41,0:38:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們聊你父親的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we spoke about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.25,0:38:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說他抗擊癌癥時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You talked about how he chose to do nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.69,0:38:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇了無所作為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when he was battling his cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.48,0:38:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他說  他可以起訴導致他得癌的公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You told him he could have fought the company that caused it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.54,0:38:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可以把這事說出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He could have told people about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.72,0:38:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可以尋求更好的治療\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He could have sought better care than what he was getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.04,0:38:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他什么都沒做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instead, he did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.06,0:38:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你父親當時的感覺跟你現在一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe your father felt the same way as you do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.82,0:38:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟  就像你說的  有什么意義呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After all, like you said, what's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.90,0:38:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這不一樣  -不一樣的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's different. - What's different
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.14,0:38:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到了選擇  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is you've found options, Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.27,0:38:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你擁有的權力  你擁有的控制權\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the power you have. That's the control you own.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.51,0:38:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想單純接受生活的安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to just take what life gives you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.10,0:38:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.65,0:38:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你究竟是怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what is going on with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.44,0:38:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不告訴我  我沒法幫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot help you if you keep me in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.07,0:38:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.77,0:39:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.25,0:39:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有黑眼圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've got bags under your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.83,0:39:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在大喊  你煩躁不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're yelling. You're jittery.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.78,0:39:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾個月來  我看著你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the last month, I have seen you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.82,0:39:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸回歸老路子  以前的行為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}slip into old patterns, old behaviors.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.14,0:39:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.04,0:39:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}刻錄  費南多·維拉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.16,0:39:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.11,0:39:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}工業氣候控制白皮書
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.76,0:40:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}室內溫度控制
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.48,0:40:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是不接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's still not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.39,0:40:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們明天問他吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we'll just have to ask him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.82,0:40:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每次播放這東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every time I try to play it or rip it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.38,0:40:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是卡住我的電腦  然后再彈出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it just freezes up my computer and spits it back out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.17,0:40:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.15,0:40:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今天在公司根本心不在焉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was acting so out of it at work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.84,0:40:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}斯黛拉·B  你得馬上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.97,0:40:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&} 今晚過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.50,0:40:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我盡量  待會兒打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.81,0:40:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you saying something, babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.36,0:40:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不對勁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.17,0:40:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該過去看看嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should I go over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.56,0:40:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And just...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.18,0:40:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Check in on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.85,0:40:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh...come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.11,0:40:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.52,0:41:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他一直都是個怪人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know he's always been a weirdo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.92,0:41:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真心擔心他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm really worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.83,0:41:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亞利桑那州的朋友弗萊德找到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Arizona buddy Fred hit me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.30,0:41:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想跟我喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants to grab a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.34,0:41:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會太久的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.98,0:41:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.10,0:42:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.05,0:42:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"深深的激情和渴望...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}"Deep passions, longing...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.38,0:42:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人從未感受到過這般的愛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the two of them had never felt such a love,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.76,0:42:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此親昵  如此心有靈犀"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}such closeness, such a connection."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.68,0:42:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有辦法不用...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Found a way to do it without--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.58,0:42:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.06,0:42:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道要如何摧毀備份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know how to take out the backups
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.51,0:42:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不必炸管線了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without blowing up the pipeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.04,0:42:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾略特  這事我們不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, Elliot, I really feel like we resolved
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.98,0:43:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經解決了嗎  你不是退出了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this thing between us. Didn't you walk away?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.97,0:43:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did. 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.73,0:43:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說  你如果走掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't I say that if you walked away,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.43,0:43:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不再是這件事的一員了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you were no longer a part of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.00,0:43:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好了一個計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a real plan--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.26,0:43:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要我再允許你加入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want me to let you back in,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.32,0:43:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得達成一定共識\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's an understanding we have to come to,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.84,0:43:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得還個債\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a debt you have to pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.24,0:43:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了  是你退出了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because, remember, you walked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.38,0:43:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不信債務這回事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you didn't believe in debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.81,0:43:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我相信債務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not true. I believe in debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.32,0:43:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信該消除債務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe in erasing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.59,0:43:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.47,0:43:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你跟我說說你父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to tell me about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.03,0:43:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別想探究我的心理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not gonna get into my head, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.64,0:43:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少給我洗腦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your David Koresh shit isn't gonna work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.74,0:43:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說他是怎么死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me how he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.20,0:43:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么意義  我覺得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why, man? Something tells me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.67,0:43:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經查過了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you already looked that shit up anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.44,0:43:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽你說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna hear it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.55,0:43:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.78,0:43:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就能回游戲廳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we go back to the arcade,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.09,0:44:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟其他人探討這個計劃嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}discuss the plan with the rest of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.86,0:44:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你指望我說什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what you want me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.74,0:44:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們本來很親近  非常親近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were close. Very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.60,0:44:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.18,0:44:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子都在邪惡公司工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Worked at Evil Corp his whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.68,0:44:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是他們最棒的電腦工程師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was one of the best computer engineers they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.43,0:44:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就被解雇了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And out of the blue, he got fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.89,0:44:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one knew why.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.54,0:44:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后有一天  他告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then one day he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.50,0:44:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他得了白血病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had leukemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.90,0:44:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還逼我不可以告訴別人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made me swear to never tell anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.01,0:44:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是我媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.69,0:44:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.47,0:44:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾個月后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few months go by...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.48,0:44:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他病得越來越重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he got sicker and sicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.27,0:44:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后  我太擔心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Finally, I got so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.18,0:44:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就告訴了我媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}told my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.37,0:44:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道后  大為光火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When he found out, he got pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.67,0:45:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我大吼大叫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Started yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.04,0:45:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我想去抱他  跟他道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember I tried to hug him, tell him I'm sorry, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.87,0:45:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他卻把我狠狠推開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}kept shoving me away and shoved me so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.65,0:45:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我跌出了窗外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I fell backwards out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.64,0:45:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把胳膊摔折了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I fell, and I broke my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.00,0:45:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他此后再也沒跟我說過話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never spoke to me after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.81,0:45:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不肯看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Couldn't even look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.93,0:45:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是他死的那晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the night he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.65,0:45:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We good?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.10,0:45:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解喪親之痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand what it's like to lose a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.21,0:45:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確令人心碎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's heartbreaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.27,0:45:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有想過或許他是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you ever think he was right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.34,0:45:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.00,0:45:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他害你摔傷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurting you that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.88,0:46:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你對他做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For what you did to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.46,0:46:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想過或許你是活該嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ever think you deserved it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.91,0:46:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒對他做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't do anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.21,0:46:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想幫他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was trying to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.63,0:46:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背叛了他的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For betraying his trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.07,0:46:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才8歲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was eight years ol--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.25,0:46:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有遵守你們的神圣約定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't commit to the sacred pact you'd formed.
